073    public static Map<Integer, Class<? extends HistoryLog>> LOG_MESSAGE_IDS = new HashMap<>();
074    public static Map<Class<? extends HistoryLog>, Integer> LOG_MESSAGE_CLASS_TO_ID = new HashMap<>();
075
076    static {
077        for (Class<? extends HistoryLog> clazz : LOG_MESSAGE_TYPES) {
078            try {
079                LOG_MESSAGE_IDS.put(clazz.newInstance().typeId(), clazz);
080                LOG_MESSAGE_CLASS_TO_ID.put(clazz, clazz.newInstance().typeId());
081            } catch (IllegalAccessException|InstantiationException e) {
082                L.e(TAG, String.format("could not instantiate %s", clazz), e);
083                e.printStackTrace();
084            }
085        }
086    }
087
088    public static HistoryLog parse(byte[] rawStream) {
089        int typeId = Bytes.readShort(rawStream, 0) & 4095;
090//        if (typeId % 256 != typeId) {
091//            L.w(TAG, "typeId "+typeId+" is being corrected to "+(typeId % 256));
092//            typeId = typeId % 256;
093//        }
094        HistoryLog ret = parseWithTypeId(rawStream, typeId);
095        if (ret instanceof UnknownHistoryLog) {
096            L.w(TAG, "retry HistoryLog parse on typeId " + typeId + " => " + ((byte) typeId));
097            HistoryLog two = parseWithTypeId(rawStream, (byte) typeId);
098            if (two instanceof UnknownHistoryLog) {
099                return ret;
100            }
101            return two;
102        }
103        return ret;
104    }
105
106    private static HistoryLog parseWithTypeId(byte[] rawStream, int typeId) {
107        HistoryLog historyLog = null;
108        if (!LOG_MESSAGE_IDS.containsKey(typeId)) {
109            L.t(TAG, "unknown HistoryLog typeId "+typeId+": "+ Hex.encodeHexString(rawStream));
110            historyLog = new UnknownHistoryLog();
111            historyLog.parse(rawStream);
112            L.i(TAG, String.format("PARSED-EMBEDDED-HISTORY-LOG(typeId=%-3d, UNKNOWN): %s", typeId, Hex.encodeHexString(rawStream)));
113            return historyLog;
114        }
115
116        try {
117            historyLog = LOG_MESSAGE_IDS.get(typeId).newInstance();
118        } catch (IllegalAccessException|InstantiationException e) {
119            L.e(TAG, "could not instantiate "+typeId, e);
120            e.printStackTrace();
121            return null;
122        }
123
124        String name = MessageHelpers.lastTwoParts(historyLog.getClass().getName());
125        L.t(TAG, "found matching "+name+" HistoryLog typeId "+typeId+": "+ Hex.encodeHexString(rawStream));
126        historyLog.parse(rawStream);
127        L.i(TAG, String.format("PARSED-EMBEDDED-HISTORY-LOG(typeId=%-3d, %s): %s", typeId, name, historyLog.toString()));
128        return historyLog;
129    }
